  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>45655</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>48724</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“冬天快到了。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>48725</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>53509</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>‘我知道该织什么了！’艾米想。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>53510</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>57604</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>‘我要织一条温暖的围巾！’</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>57605</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>63374</EndMilliseconds>
