  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>104197</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>107958</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“天啊！”她叫道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>107959</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>113776</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我的围巾上有很多地方织错了！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>113777</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>119672</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你的围巾还是很漂亮。”妈妈说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>119673</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>124106</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我喜欢紫色的毛线。”爸爸说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>124107</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>130084</EndMilliseconds>
