  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>139136</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>145985</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>‘我再也不想织围巾了。’艾米想。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>145986</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>152478</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>一天早上，奥利弗看起来很伤心。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>152479</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>155432</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他的眼里充满了泪水。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>155433</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>159557</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“怎么了，奥利弗？”艾米问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>159558</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>166525</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“今天学校办‘紫色的一天’活动。”奥利弗说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>166526</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>172939</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“但是我没有任何紫色的东西。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>172940</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>179724</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“嗯……”艾米跑回自己的房间。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>179725</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>185144</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“给你，奥利弗。”艾米说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>185145</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>187943</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你可以戴我的围巾。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>33</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>187944</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>191856</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>奥利弗接过艾米的围巾。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>34</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>191857</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>196236</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“这是紫色的！”奥利弗喊。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>35</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>196237</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>199430</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他把它围在脖子上。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>36</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>199431</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>208912</EndMilliseconds>
